===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{context|chiefly|UK|Ireland|Australia|New Zealand|lang=en}} A period of [[fourteen]] nights; two [[week]]s.

===Adverb===
{{en-adv|-}}

# After a fortnight has passed.
#: '''1852''' [http://www.gutenberg.org/dirs/etext97/blkhs12.txt Charles Dickens, ''Bleak House'']: ''We will proceed with the hearing on Wednesday '''fortnight'''''.

